---
title: African-Inspired Peanut and Beyond Meat® Soup with Kidney Beans and Sesame Flatbreads
description: Rich peanut butter and fibre-loaded kidney beans and Beyond Meat® make for a creamy and oh-so-filling soup! The golden sesame seed flatbreads are perfect for dipping, too! This one's a keeper for those days when you want to go veggie.
